  ('food-tech-moex-00459', 'food-tech', 'food-tech-moex-112-9af4f2a0', 'sub-food-tech-01', NULL, 'essay', '某品管員採用凱氏定氮法（Kjeldahlmethod）測定粗蛋白質含量，樣品重
